    Oregon Fishing License and Regulation Summary
</h2>
<ul>
    <li>
        <strong>Angling License Required</strong> for ages 12+.
    </li>
    <li>
        <strong>No trout tag required</strong> for stocked lake harvest.
    </li>
    <li>
        <strong>Catch-and-release only</strong> for wild trout in many rivers.
    </li>
    <li>
        <strong>Free Fishing Weekends</strong>: No license needed—offered several times yearly by ODFW.
    </li>
</ul>
<p>
    Always review the latest rules at myodfw.com.
